    "description": "<strong>Hedgehot - Battle Strike :</strong>  Cards in which reside magical creatures are used to challenge other users and pave a way to the top.<br><br><br>Hedgehot - Battle Strike is a 1 versus 1 Card Game similar to the likes of Heartstone or Runeterra, where using your cards, brain and stamina, you try to defeat your opponent and bring their life points to 0.<br><br><strong>Features : </strong> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Friendly Battle - Invite your friends in a lobby to challenge them to prove your skills.<br></li><li> Online MatchMaking - Find or create a lobby for random players around the world to challenge you. Best place to refine your skills.<br></li><li> Deck Builder - Choose your favorite cards to challenge others with.<br></li><li> Shop - Purchase cards to upgrade your deck and create the best possible Meta.</li></ul><br><br><strong>Community : </strong><br>You may join the Hedgehot - Battle Strike official discord to find other battlers and a place to share your experience! ",
